== Classification of the document
=== Objective
This document sums up examples in interacting with the provider API. 

=== Target group

The document is aimed at software developers who are involved in implementing a client that interacts with the provider API of the VZD-FHIR-Directory.

== FHIRDirectoryProviderAPI
To access the provider API a valid provider access_token is needed that can be obtained by authenticating via link:FHIR_VZD_HOWTO_Authenticate.adoc#22-authenticate-for-the-provider-api[Provider Authenticate].

=== Query API Information
This operation returns generell API information and no authentication is needed.

.Request
[source]
----
curl  -X GET \
  'https://fhir-directory-ref.vzd.ti-dienste.de/tim-provider-services/' \
  --header 'Accept: */*'
----

.Response Content
[source]
----
{
  "title": "I_VZD_TIM_Provider_Services",
  "description": "REST Schnittstelle zur Abfrage der Föderationsliste und zur Administration der TI-Messenger Domänen.",
  "version": "1.3.6"
}
----

=== Query MXID Location
This operation returns the location of the MXID. 

.Request
[source]
----
curl -X GET "[baseUrl]/tim-provider-services/localization?mxid=%401-2arvtst-ap000037%3Atim.test.gematik.de' -H 'Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJFUzI1NiJ9..gThvA77gnbQAAtDYCj9THKc8DzKdR6afOkrgldKEgspOohGU6LFdQ5KsMEkkzJ1-g2oAl6rSGa4Drhz7oIrZ9g"
----

.Response Content
[source]
----
"org"
----

=== Add own domain
This operation adds a new domain to the federation list.

==== Example for adding a domain for healthcare professionals

.Request
[source]
----
curl  -X POST \
  '[baseUrl]/tim-provider-services/federation' \
  --header 'Accept: */*' \
  --header 'User-Agent: Thunder Client (https://www.thunderclient.com)' \
  --header 'Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJCUDI1NlIxIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0..MN77Ar9JhuY8c1Qp_kHuWA2E8pFIO2btralTmJXqaOYYqHGxLZtISd_ybu-NbhI5Y3LWc6M7FP4Jg6ltqSxj_Q' \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --data-raw '{
  "domain": "matrix.test.service-ti.de",
  "telematikID": "MY-SMC-B-Testkarte",
  "isInsurance": false
}'
----

.Response Content
[source]
----
{
  "domain": "matrix.test.service-ti.de",
  "telematikID": "MY-SMC-B-Testkarte",
  "isInsurance": false
}
----

==== Example for adding a domain that provides accounts of health insured persons
.Request
[source]
----
curl  -X POST \
  '[baseUrl]/tim-provider-services/federation' \
  --header 'Accept: */*' \
  --header 'User-Agent: Thunder Client (https://www.thunderclient.com)' \
  --header 'Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJCUDI1NlIxIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0..MN77Ar9JhuY8c1Qp_kHuWA2E8pFIO2btralTmJXqaOYYqHGxLZtISd_ybu-NbhI5Y3LWc6M7FP4Jg6ltqSxj_Q' \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --data-raw '{
  "domain": "matrix.test.service-ti.de",
  "telematikID": "5-2-KHAUS-Kornfeld01",
  "isInsurance": true,
  "ik": [101108153]
}''
----

.Response Content
[source]
----
{
    "domain": "matrix.test.service-ti.de",
    "telematikID": "5-2-KHAUS-Kornfeld01",
    "isInsurance": true,
    "ik": [
        "101108153"
    ]
}
----

==== Additional constraints for the ik number(s)
- ik starts with 10 or 16 or 95
- ik is based on 9 numbers
- ik must be set in case isInsurance=true
- ik must not be set in case isInsurance=false
- ik has to be unique in the federation list
- the check digit based on chapter 1.2.5 must be correct (https://www.gkv-datenaustausch.de/media/dokumente/leistungserbringer_1/sonstige_leistungserbringer/GR-IK-2023-11.pdf)

==== Example for adding a domain with redirects
To enable a correct discovery of the userinfo endpoint, redirect domains might need to be added to the allowlist of the firewall protecting the vzd-fhir directory. Please see link:FHIR_VZD_HOWTO_Authenticate.adoc#21-authenticate-for-the-search-endpoint-with-your-homeserver-login[Search Authenticate] for details.

.Request
[source]
----
curl  -X POST \
  '[baseUrl]/tim-provider-services/federation' \
  --header 'Accept: */*' \
  --header 'User-Agent: Thunder Client (https://www.thunderclient.com)' \
  --header 'Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJCUDI1NlIxIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0..MN77Ar9JhuY8c1Qp_kHuWA2E8pFIO2btralTmJXqaOYYqHGxLZtISd_ybu-NbhI5Y3LWc6M7FP4Jg6ltqSxj_Q' \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --data-raw '{
  "domain": "ti-messengertest6.dev.ccs.gematik.solutions",
  "telematikID": "5-2-KHAUS-Kornfeld01",
  "isInsurance": false,
  "redirectDomains":["redirect1.ti-messenger.gematik.de", "redirect2.ti-messenger.gematik.de"]
}'
----

.Response Content
[source]
----
{
    "domain": "ti-messengertest6.dev.ccs.gematik.solutions",
    "telematikID": "5-2-KHAUS-Kornfeld01",
    "isInsurance": false,
    "redirectDomains": [
        "redirect1.ti-messenger.gematik.de",
        "redirect2.ti-messenger.gematik.de"
    ]
}
----

=== Check own managed domains
This operation returns the own domains that are marked as "inactive".

.Request
----
curl -X GET \
  'https://fhir-directory-ref.vzd.ti-dienste.de/tim-provider-services/federationCheck' \
  --header 'Accept: */*' \
  --header 'User-Agent: Thunder Client (https://www.thunderclient.com)' \
  --header 'Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJFUzI1NiJ9..g-TOcYRmT64grzhQUKsdCXXJ0wH3WSQuVQwPAh6PrvQecJFPDcOqjOba-ojcUBWeIgT4lZBwGIjC4uBNMTKL4w'
----

.Response Content
[source]
----
{
  "inactiveOrganizationDomains": [
    {
      "domain": "testserver.service-ti.de",
      "telematikID": "1-1gemref-testowner-0001",
      "isInsurance": false,
      "redirectDomains": []
    }
  ]
}
----
